What:          /sys/devices/platform/110f0000.drmdp/drm-displayport/dp_hotplug_error_code
Date:          September 2023
KernelVersion: 5.15
Contact:       "Sergey Volk" <servolk@google.com>
Description:
               Used to pass error code associated with a hotplug event sent to client.
               Zero indicates successful hotplug event, non-zero value indicates hotplug failure.

