What:		/sys/devices/platform/110f0000.drmdp/drm-displayport-stats/edid_invalid_failures
Date:		November 2023
KernelVersion:	5.15
Contact:	"Weizhung Ding" <weizhungding@google.com>
Description:
		Used to count the number of edid invalid failures. If EDID is invalid, the count
		will be increased.

What:		/sys/devices/platform/110f0000.drmdp/drm-displayport-stats/sink_count_invalid_failures
Date:		November 2023
KernelVersion:	5.15
Contact:	"Weizhung Ding" <weizhungding@google.com>
Description:
		Used to count the number of sink count invalid failures. If sink count is invalid,
		the count will be increased.

What:		/sys/devices/platform/110f0000.drmdp/drm-displayport-stats/link_unstable_failures
Date:		November 2023
KernelVersion:	5.15
Contact:	"Weizhung Ding" <weizhungding@google.com>
Description:
		Used to count the number of link unstable failures. When DP link is down and re-establish
		the link, the count will be increased.
